<div1 type="letter">

<pb facs="nei.j4b.9.129.131.001" />
<fw type="curatorial">129</fw>
<note type="curatorial"></note>

<opener>
<dateline>10-20-'32
Peru Nebr.
</dateline>
<salute>Sweet girl,</salute>
</opener>

<p>Just rec'd your two letters 70 Pate! I was so happy to read ^more letters from you! Had no notion I'd receive two! You dear girl - I love you endlessly, &amp; do know how you feel in regard to Curran!
Please, sweetheart - in case a sudden &amp; unexpected happen-ing should <del>pl</del> take place with him - I want you to</p>

<fw type="curatorial">130</fw>
<fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>

<p>
remember &amp; know that I am in deep sympathy with you &amp; love you! 
I do hope that my true love for you, der girl, will help to brace you up under those or any other circumstances! This is a rushed letter, but I am missing you so - that I could write a thousand letters without satisfying myself! Always I love you, &amp; your thoughtfulness in writing me is everything to me!</p>
<closer>
<salute>Always Love,</salute>
<signed> Sig.</signed>
<note></note>
</closer>

</div1>

